content.text:
Let me analyze the images and provide a detailed solution:

Main Target Image Analysis:
- Total Blocks: 8 blocks
- Colors Used: Green, Yellow, Orange/Red
- Layers: 3-4 layers in the main structure
- Two structures: A tall multi-layered structure and a smaller house-like structure

Block Dictionary Mapping:
Required Blocks:
- Green Block (Index 5 or 6): Vertical rectangular green block
- Yellow Block (Index 8): Horizontal rectangular yellow block
- Orange/Red Rectangular Block (Index 9): Vertical orange/red block
- Orange/Red Triangular Block (Index 13 or 15): Triangular orange/red block

Assembly Instructions:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 5 (green vertical block)
    Step2: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal block) on top of green block
    Step3: Move block with index 9 (orange vertical block) next to green block
    Step4: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal block) on top of orange block
    Step5: Move block with index 13 (orange triangular block) on top of the structure
    Step6: For smaller structure, use block index 5 (green), index 8 (yellow), index 13 (orange triangular)
}
